text: Club Atlético Banfield is an Argentine sports club located from Banfield, Buenos Aires. It is mostly known for its football team. ==Honours== *Primera División (1): 2009 Apertura *Copa de Honor Municipalidad de Buenos Aires (1): 1920 *Primera B Nacional (3): 1992–93, 2000–01, 2013–14 *Primera B Metropolitana (7): 1899, 1900, 1919, 1939, 1946, 1962, 1973 Category:Football clubs in Buenos Aires Category:1896 establishments Category:1890s establishments in Argentina
title: C.A. Banfield
